2002-01-20  Seth Nickell  <snickell@stanford.edu>

	* configure.in: 
	* NEWS
	Bump version to 1.0.4, update NEWS to reflect this.

2002-01-17  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-mime.h: Remove include of <regex.h>.

2002-01-14  Andy Hertzfeld  <andy@differnet.com>

	fixed synchronization problems by adding a routine to reset the
	response buffer, and using it when to start a command.  Also,
	made a few minor formatting fixes.
	
	* modules/nntp-method.c: (do_control_write),
	(nntp_connection_reset_buffer), (do_basic_command),
	(load_file_fragment), (prepare_to_read_file), (do_open):

2002-01-13  Andy Hertzfeld  <andy@differnet.com>

	checkin of new nntp-method for gnome-vfs, which allows binary files
	from newsgroups to be viewed and manipulated from nautilus.  See
	http://differnet.com/nntp for a more thorough description.
	
	* modules/Makefile.am:
	added nntp-method files
	
	* modules/default-modules.conf:
	added nntp prootocol
	
	* modules/nntp-method.c: (nntp_response_to_vfs_result),
	(read_response_line), (get_response), (do_control_write),
	(do_basic_command), (nntp_connection_create),
	(nntp_connection_destroy), (my_str_hash), (my_str_equal),
	(nntp_connection_uri_hash), (nntp_connection_uri_equal),
	(nntp_connection_acquire), (nntp_connection_release),
	(is_number_or_space), (all_numbers_or_spaces),
	(remove_numbers_between_dashes), (remove_number_at_end),
	(trim_nonalpha_chars), (remove_of_expressions),
	(filter_folder_name), (remove_commas), (is_number),
	(parse_date_string), (parse_header), (nntp_fragment_new),
	(nntp_fragment_destroy), (map_slashes), (nntp_file_new),
	(nntp_file_destroy), (nntp_file_look_up_fragment),
	(nntp_file_get_total_size), (nntp_file_add_part), (look_up_file),
	(start_loading_article), (uu_decode_text), (base_64_map),
	(base_64_decode_text), (line_in_decode_range), (load_from_article),
	(load_file_fragment), (bytes_in_buffer), (copy_bytes_from_buffer),
	(nntp_file_read), (free_nntp_file_list),
	(get_files_from_newsgroup), (strip_slashes),
	(extract_newsgroup_and_filename), (nntp_file_from_uri),
	(has_all_fragments), (add_file_fragment), (remove_partial_files),
	(update_file_sizes), (add_file_to_folder), (remove_file_from_list),
	(remove_contained_files), (calculate_folder_mod_date),
	(generate_folder_from_element), (generate_folders),
	(destroy_element), (destroy_folder_hash), (assemble_folders),
	(assemble_files_from_overview), (do_is_local),
	(prepare_to_read_file), (do_open), (do_close), (do_read),
	(do_get_file_info), (do_get_file_info_from_handle),
	(do_open_directory), (do_close_directory), (do_read_directory),
	(do_check_same_fs), (vfs_module_init), (vfs_module_shutdown)
	
	this is the implementation of the nntp-method
	
	* modules/nntp-method.h:
	structure definitions for nntp-method
	
2002-01-04  Pablo Saratxaga <pablo@mandrakesoft.com>

	* configure,in (ALL_LINGUAS): Added "eu".

2001-11-13  Frederic Crozat  <fcrozat@mandrakesoft.com>

	* configure.in:

	Fix default detection of OpenSSL libraries

2001-11-09  Seth Nickell  <snickell@stanford.edu>

	* configure.in:

	Depend on gnome-mime-data.
	
	* Makefile.am:

	Don't build data.
	
	* data/Makefile.am:
	* data/mime/ChangeLog:
	* data/mime/Makefile.am:
	* data/mime/WHERE_IS_THE_MIME_REGISTRY:
	* data/mime/gnome-vfs-mime-magic:
	* data/mime/gnome-vfs.applications:
	* data/mime/gnome-vfs.keys.in:
	* data/mime/gnome-vfs.mime:

	Remove the MIME database from GnomeVFS. The actual
	data is now stored in the module 'gnome-mime-data'.
	This allows the information to be shared between
	GnomeVFS1 and GnomeVFS2.
	
	* doc/tmpl/gnome-vfs-unused.sgml:

	Some strange documentation change.
	
2001-10-30  Maciej Stachowiak  <mjs@noisehavoc.org>

	* modules/Makefile.am, modules/default-modules.conf,
	modules/gconf-method.c, modules/gconf-method.h: Remove gconf
	method.

2001-10-25  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* configure.in: Don't generate Makefiles in the intl and macros
	subdirectories, since we don't compile in them.

2001-10-24  Havoc Pennington  <hp@redhat.com>

	* modules/file-method.c (get_stat_info): fix memory leak of
	file_info->symlink_name for multiply-nested symlinks, and avoid 
	infinite loop for symlink cycles. Bug #62494

2001-10-24  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* gnome-vfs.spec.in: Fix include directories (thanks Toralf Lund)

2001-10-20  Anders Carlsson  <andersca@gnu.org>

	* configure.in (ALL_LINGUAS): Don't use commas here.

2001-10-15  Eskil Heyn Olsen  <eskil@eskil.dk>

	* configure.in:
	Add all the extra libs (xml, oaf, gconf) to the gnome-vfs-config
	and vfsConf.sh scripts.

2001-10-12  Maciej Stachowiak  <mjs@noisehavoc.org>

	* NEWS, configure.in: Updated for 1.0.3.

	* modules/Makefile.am: Rename unused SOURCES variables to SRCLIST
	for Automake 1.5 compatibility. Patch from Ali Akcaagac
	<ali.akcaagac@stud.fh-wilhelmshaven.de>.

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-backend.c (gnome_vfs_backend_loadinit):
	Pass NULL instead of LIBDIR so LD_LIBRARY_PATH is searched and
	thus make distcheck passes.

2001-10-10  jacob berkman  <jacob@ximian.com>

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-backend.c (gnome_vfs_backend_loadinit):
	fix a thinko

	* libgnomevfs-corba/Makefile.am (libgnomevfs_corba_la_LDFLAGS): 
	* libgnomevfs-pthread/Makefile.am
	(libgnomevfs_pthread_la_LDFLAGS): build with -module
	-avoid-version

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-backend.c (gnome_vfs_backend_loadinit):
	fix a buffer overflow, and use g_module_build_path() so we work on
	hp-ux.  fixes gnome bug #51966

	* libgnomevfs/Makefile.am: remove an extraneous space

	* gnome-vfs.spec.in: include the module .so files in the main
	package, and don't include their .la or .a files (since they can't
	be used anyway)

2001-10-07  Maciej Stachowiak  <mjs@noisehavoc.org>

	* configure.in: Fixed bug 41957 (gnome-vfs config does not reject
	libxml 2) by copying the check for libxml 1.x from the nautiluse
	configure script. This change should not be merged to HEAD.

2001-10-07  Maciej Stachowiak  <mjs@noisehavoc.org>

	* modules/nfs-method.c: (rpc_init_tcp): Fix bug 55805 (mistake in
	gnome-vfs/modules/nfs-method.c), patch from Martin Pool
	<mbp@samba.org>.

	* doc/tmpl/gnome-vfs-unused.sgml: Mystery doc updates.

2001-09-30  Anders Carlsson  <andersca@gnu.org>

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-module-callback.c:
	(gnome_vfs_module_callback_free_stack_info): Free the stack info
	structure too.

2001-09-31  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@gnome.org>

	* configure.in: Added "pt" to ALL_LINGUAS.
	
2001-09-28  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* configure.in: Oops. My mistake. I confused gnome-vfs versions
	with Nautilus versions. Back to 1.0.2.

2001-09-28  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* configure.in: Update version number to 1.0.5. The people doing
	releases haven't been updating versions, it seems.

2001-09-20  Havoc Pennington  <hp@redhat.com>

	* modules/file-method.c (find_trash_in_hierarchy): remove the
	trash search stuff
	(create_trash_near): ditto

	* modules/Makefile.am, desktop-method.c, desktop-module.conf: Add
	desktop method for desktop URIs such as start-here

