2001-01-09  Pavel Cisler  <pavel@eazel.com>

	reviewed by: Darin Adler  <darin@eazel.com>

	Fixed 5398 (Async callbacks need to be passed over ownership of data)

	* libgnomevfs-pthread/gnome-vfs-async-ops.c: (async_open),
