	(make_request), (make_propfind_request), (vfs_module_init),
	(vfs_module_shutdown):

	HTTP module now supports HTTP proxies.  HTTP proxy is gotten from GConf
	key /system/gnome-vfs/http-proxy.  This makes the HTTP module dependent
	on GConf. 	

