	(gnome_vfs_new_directory_with_unique_name):
	Darin and mjs hated the old name.

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-xfer.c: 
	(gnome_vfs_xfer_delete_items):
	New call to support a fallback delete for files that cannot be moved
	to Trash.

