	* libgnomevfs-corba/gnome-vfs-slave-notify.c
	(impl_Notify_open_as_channel): cast "struct sockaddr_un *"
	argument to connect to "struct sockaddr *".

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-private.h: Fix the getdelim prototype.

