2000-01-27  John Sullivan  <sullivan@eazel.com>

	Moved, renamed, and made public GnomeVFSFileInfo-comparing routines.

	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-file-info.c:
	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-file-info.h:
